OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInflation pushes UK debt   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finterest to August record  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Soaring inflation led interest costs on
OL,6, UK government debt to hit a new record 
OL,7, for August.                            
OL,9,FInterest due reached #8.2bn during the 
OL,10,Fmonth, #1.5bn more than last year and  
OL,11,Fthe highest August figure since records
OL,12,Fbegan in 1997, the Office for National 
OL,13,FStatistics (ONS) said.                 
OL,15,FThe high interest payments come as the 
OL,16,Fgovernment prepares to borrow billions 
OL,17,Fto help households with energy bills.  
OL,19,FIt will also reportedly unveil #30bn of
OL,20,Ftax cuts in a mini-Budget on Friday.   
